    "description": "<strong>Dinosaurs roam the earth once more...</strong><br><br>In Primal Omen, you must investigate a remote tropical island and discover why it is overrun with dinosaurs. They are fierce, intelligent and extremely dangerous. Your resources will be limited. Tread carefully, listen and feel your surroundings - you will need every edge you can get in order to survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Modern Survival Horror Experience - 3rd person atmospheric resource scarce horror awaits.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/65a6c0cb7b6efcdc22565ddb7fe63add.poster.avif?t=1702683444\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/65a6c0cb7b6efcdc22565ddb7fe63add.webm?t=1702683444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/65a6c0cb7b6efcdc22565ddb7fe63add.mp4?t=1702683444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    </li><li>Minimal Diegetic HUD - Want to check your remaining ammo? Stop and check your weapon, Your Health? How does your character look?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/4610cf4dc40d8eec3b94140eefe37123.poster.avif?t=1702683444\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/4610cf4dc40d8eec3b94140eefe37123.webm?t=1702683444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/4610cf4dc40d8eec3b94140eefe37123.mp4?t=1702683444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    </li><li>Epic and Terrifying Beasts - Dinosaurs of all shapes and sizes stalk you, humans are no longer the hunters - they are the hunted<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/994b0c5c2282162bd0ba8334e3c8a63d.poster.avif?t=1702683444\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/994b0c5c2282162bd0ba8334e3c8a63d.webm?t=1702683444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865710/extras/994b0c5c2282162bd0ba8334e3c8a63d.mp4?t=1702683444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    </li><li>A wide arsenal of weapons and gear to find, buy and upgrade - Spend rare resources to make sure your gear is as best as it can be<br>    </li><li>An island full of dark secrets - Explore a living breathing lush tropical island, and discover secret facilities within</li></ul>",
